WEBVTT

00:14:25.720 --> 00:14:30.773
of the chances for a long,
healthy, fulfilling life.

00:14:31.464 --> 00:14:34.151
When immigrants send money
or goods home to their family,

00:14:34.175 --> 00:14:37.324
it plays a significant role
in narrowing these gaps,

00:14:37.348 --> 00:14:39.391
if a very incomplete one.

00:14:39.771 --> 00:14:42.806
It does more than all
of the foreign aid programs

00:14:42.830 --> 00:14:44.813
in the world combined.

00:14:46.778 --> 00:14:49.349
We began with the nativist questions,

00:14:49.373 --> 00:14:51.983
about immigrants as tools,

00:14:52.007 --> 00:14:53.618
as others

00:14:53.642 --> 00:14:54.983
and as parasites.

00:14:55.666 --> 00:14:59.156
Where might these new questions
about worker rights,

00:14:59.180 --> 00:15:00.777
about responsibility